    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Pass through a hallway and arrive where you started.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Climb a staircase and watch the wall become the floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leave a cube in one spot and return to it from somewhere else.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Superspective is a first-person puzzle game set in a seamless, non-Euclidean space that is governed by logic, but not the kind you’re used to. Experience firsthand the majesty of impossibility.</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are no tutorials, no dialogue, no signs telling you what to do. Just you, an abstract world, and the quiet sense that something may be observing you.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239490/extras/b63aa76c574d8598caa3659577669b01.avif?t=1747512337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239490/extras_big/b63aa76c574d8598caa3659577669b01.avif?t=1747512337 width=800 height=116 /></span>You can expect to...</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore a seamless, non-Euclidean world where space folds, loops, repeats, and at every turn defies expectation.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239490/extras/efe2493895fab4f61fb276462c2e3f21.avif?t=1747512337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239490/extras_big/efe2493895fab4f61fb276462c2e3f21.avif?t=1747512337 width=800 height=453 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover that gravity is relative; direction is a matter of perspective.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239490/extras/337e70656ae1fd57de75897ef421d84a.avif?t=1747512337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239490/extras_big/337e70656ae1fd57de75897ef421d84a.avif?t=1747512337 width=800 height=452 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Lose yourself in an abstract, surreal environment of clean lines, geometric architecture, and stark visual contrasts.<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239490/extras/5b3fdb63112ece74de8e398731f802b8.avif?t=1747512337\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2239490/extras_big/5b3fdb63112ece74de8e398731f802b8.avif?t=1747512337 width=800 height=453 /></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Solve spatial puzzles that reward careful observation and unconventional thinking.</p></li></ul>",
